title: Semi-automatic patch tape fixing machine US-XYT-300
title_uz: Yarim-avtomatik paket tutqichining yamoq qismini yopishtirish uskunasi US-XYT-300

title_en: Semi-automatic patch tape fixing machine US-XYT-300
short_description: This US-XYT-300 model equipment serves to fix the patch on the package handle and is semi-automatic. The equipment has a processing speed of up to 20 packets per minute. The weight of the equipment is 350 kg, the voltage is 380/220V, and the total size is 1.65 * 1.56 * 1.24 m.

Uskuna daqiqasiga 20 tagacha paketga ishlov berish tezligiga ega. Vazni 350 kg ni tashkil qiluvchi uskunaning kuchlanishi 380/220V va umumiy o'lchami 1.65 * 1.56 * 1.24 m ni tashkil qiladi.

long_description:
